posting_body: ['Lofts at Farmers Market', 'Featured Floorplan: 1-bed / 1-bath / 847 sq ft', 'Monthly Rent: $1810', 'Deposit: Call', 'show contact info', 'Description: Life can get busy and stressful, and this is precisely why the place that you call home is so important.', 'When you have a quiet, safe, and beautiful place to put your feet up at the end of a long day, it makes facing tomorrow that much easier.', 'The Lofts at Farmers Market strives to create a peaceful oasis in the heart of Saint Paul, Minnesota where you can relax, refresh, and rejuvenate.', 'Lease Terms: 3-Month, 4-Month, 5-Month, 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month, 14-Month, 15-Month, 16-Month', 'Pet Policy: Dogs and cats welcome: Max. 2 allowed per home, deposit $200, one-time fee $200, monthly rent $40.', 'No weight limit, breed restrictions apply.', 'Apartment Amenities:', '● Air Conditioning', '● Big Windows', '● Granite Countertops', '● High Ceilings', '● Linen Closet*', 'In Select Homes', '● Microwave', '● Pantry*', 'In Select Homes', '● Patio/Balcony*', 'In Select Homes', '● Washer/Dryer Full Size in Every Home', '● Window Coverings', 'Community Features:', '● Accepts Credit Card Payments', '● Bicycle Storage', '● Fitness Center', '● Free Weight Equipment', '● Onsite Management', '● Outdoor Dining Area', '● Pet Friendly', '● Planned Community Activities', '● Social Events', '● Weight Machines', '● 24 Hour Availability', '● 24-Hour Fitness Center', '● Bike Repair Stations', '● Community-Wide WiFi', '● Dry Cleaning Service Available', '● Kingsley Excellence Award', '● Pet Washing Station', '● Property Manager on Site', '● Reservable Clubhouse', '● Resident Lounge/ Clubroom', 'Call us:', 'show contact info', '260 5th St E', 'St. Paul, MN 55101', 'Tue - Fri: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM', 'Sat: 10:00 AM - 4:00 PM', 'Website:', '<URL>', 'Please note pricing and availability subject to change.', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY', '91F292BECB024B']
